description:
Chase is a very sweet, calm, low-key guy. He just seems to take everything in stride.
“Doesn’t anything ever upset you?” I asked.
“Nah,” he replied. “Life’s too short to get worked up over stupid shit!”
He’s 29 now and he’s already had a pretty interesting life.
“School wasn’t really for me, so I joined the military.”
“How was that?”
“It was a great experience,” he said. “I got to travel all over the world. Australia, Hong Kong, Sinapore...”
“What are you up to now?”
“Basically just school full time,” he said.
He also likes to work out a lot, and it’s paid off. Check out his muscles!
title: Chase
